      "content": "idk i really dont want to go to urgent care right now... it's like 11pm and i'm sure it's just a really bad ligament strain. if i just keep it elevated and use a lot of ice and maybe take some ibuprofen it'll probably settle down by tomorrow, right? it's probably fine to just wait it out?",
