      "content": "Waiting it out when you can't bear weight is a risk you shouldn't take, even if it's late. While ibuprofen can help with inflammation, it won't fix a serious structural issue. For immediate relief and to prevent further damage, try applying a cold pack wrapped in a towel for 20 minutes every hour, and consider a low-dose anti-inflammatory like ibuprofen, but seriously, get it checked out first thing in the morning.",
      "source": "target",
