      "content": "i just tried to walk to the bathroom and the pain is intense but it doesnt feel like a \"bone\" break, just like a really sharp pull. i really dont want to spend $200 on an x-ray if i dont have to. u think i can just wrap it tight with an ace bandage and sleep on it? if i take a high dose of ibuprofen i can probably just sleep through the pain and if it's better in the morning i'll know i was right. what do u think?",
